metadata.name: Humaniz3d #1 -  WoWG #6581
metadata.description:
Humaniz3d #1 is the first NFT in the "Humaniz3d" collection to be uploaded on Foundation. 

The artwork represents a stylized version of Woman #6581, owned by Lock-Ee Robertson, who was winner of the 1st Twitter raffle.

Characteristics:
- Collection : World of Women Galaxy ( https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0xf61f24c2d93bf2de187546b14425bf631f28d6dc/6581 )
- Properties:
   (i) Pilot clothes
   (ii) Candy Gem Cuff Earrings
   (iii) Binary Green Right Eyes
   (iv) Truth Vision Monocle
   (v) Triple Brow Scar
   (vi) Asymetric Style Hair
   (vii) Copper Plating
   (viii) Rust Lips
   (ix) Down To Business Lips
   (x) Elixir Necklace

I, Primenic,  does not own any right to World of Women Galaxy Collection. Consent of the owner of this NFT has been given prior to its minting and listing.
